com.camerontec.catalys.util.service

Class ServiceRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.catalys.util.service.ServiceRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<IService>

    public final class ServiceRegistry
extends Object
implements Iterable<IService>
    Singleton which manages a collection of IService objects, indexed by the service's name (IService.getServiceName()).

    This implementation guarantees that iteration order is the same as insertion order.

    This class is thread-safe, including in the presence of concurrent modifications in one thread and iteration in another.
